{"tid":1727811,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好掛住圍爐，我哋文宣唔夠，黎明都要有焦點","createTime":"2019-11-16T14:47:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T15:10:09.000Z","uid":162060,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"cfc1f5a60d603067cfc35d8cd851d8d40f246f51","tid":1727811,"uid":162060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:47:04.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">唔好再同我講贏到趴街，<br />\n民意歸邊嗰啲<br />\n香港人善忘唔係第一日既事<br />\n<br />\n依家調查已經有<br />\n<ins>四成人</ins><br />\n覺得示威者要對暴力升級負責任<br />\n<br />\n政府同建制派就攞住個機會不斷做選舉工程同打民意戰</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">文宣啊！<br />\n文宣啊！<br />\n文宣啊！</div></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黎明行動去到曙光旭日<br />\n有冇發覺除左擾民之外<br />\n其實冇好大實際功效？<br />\n<br />\n唔搞狗<br />\n唔搞狗竇<br />\n唔搞狗官<br />\n等班狗繼續射tg污染香港<br />\n封路搞唔到班有錢人（市照開 樓照升）<br />\n個市第四第五日冇跌過<br />\n愈黎愈多人鬧塞鐵<br />\n<br />\n到最後反而搞到普羅大眾<br />\n<br />\n再用同一方式打多7日好多人會厭倦<br />\n佔中就係因為咁死<br />\n補選就係因為咁死<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">唔好同我講歸曬邊嗰啲<br />\n<br />\n今日民賤聯主動出黎清rb<br />\n就係做緊選舉工程<br />\n政府繼續區選<br />\n就係證明佢哋覺得有勝算<br />\n選舉係以人頭計，唔係喺中環好多人拍手就代表夠<br />\n<br />\n中環區不嘍就輸選舉<br />\n依家仲搞埋其他區</span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">話區選冇用嗰啲<br />\n區選就係表達民意基礎<br />\n唔係打咗咁耐就想咁樣打爛下話？<br />\n每一役都要贏</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n三罷可以繼續做，但係唔該俾人覺得三罷有用先得<br />\n冇人會鍾意俾人逼做任何嘢<br />\n<br />\n黎明要聚焦、<br />\n擾民要最低化、<br />\n文宣快啲同我刷，<br />\n民心永遠係唔會夠。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">每一役都要贏<br />\n文宣！！！</div></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n話我左膠撚民意撚散水撚既請睇以下：<br />\n<br />\n點解成日講民意對場運動咁重要<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1725296\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1725296</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c710467113596b19eba6c20907ce11aa696085b0","tid":1727811,"uid":162060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:47:34.000Z","msg":"自推一陣"},{"pid":"f54454e20624e999c894cfd365805e487d767824","tid":1727811,"uid":162060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:47:48.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d70d3b2b91365656bcda795469d6ab59c7ec5f28","tid":1727811,"uid":162060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:48:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5e5b25b25f7b7124519badbfd6660d1248e15a43","tid":1727811,"uid":162060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:48:17.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8db37d1fa6c01af1a82f34dc1c3fd725a85f5df1","tid":1727811,"uid":162060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:48:36.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d722636ce5b5fb92ee7346ad3babdc898856205a","tid":1727811,"uid":162060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:48:52.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2fd40e8f188313325e046d30528a7086cd795979","tid":1727811,"uid":162060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:49:05.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d9a51a0472a5392895e030c07edd2e8f2d3b261b","tid":1727811,"uid":162060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:49:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"134304c90a14235a9ed36f974d138c3c09ee4662","tid":1727811,"uid":162060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:49:43.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"741e5fdfaaae68b0403e523dadb4db6cd0affe2e","tid":1727811,"uid":162060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:50:03.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5fbd5e328eeb907f09a184b2cbdb808bb77d1438","tid":1727811,"uid":162060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:50:22.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"090e326d2f4e0aba89a6b84bb7